    "facility": "GKN Aerospace, Garden Grove, CA",
    "started_iso": "2026-05-21T22:40:00Z",
    "status_headline": "Incident resolved \u2014 all evacuation orders lifted May 27 at 7:30 PM PDT. GKN Aerospace SVP Steve Carlin issues formal apology: \"We are sorry for the uncertainty and disruption this situation has caused.\" Hundreds of residents demand accountability and GKN closure. GGUSD 12 campuses reopened today for final day of school year. Hazmat crews continue treating solidified MMA in 300-ft exclusion zone on Western Ave. DA criminal investigation and class-action lawsuits ongoing.",
